overview: Good service is hard to find, but our Bare Tenders are ready to wait on your every raw need! Sean Xavier and Ruslan Angelo celebrate a big tip with more than just the tip. Damon Heart catches the wait staff, Ace Era and Devin Franco, screwing in his hotel room. Alejandro Castillo goes above and beyond as to wait on Devin Franco and Sean Xavier. With the hotel all to themselves, the Bare Tenders Ruslan Angelo, Rico Marlon, Scott DeMarco, Sebastian Oliver, Daniel Azcona throw an orgy!
title: Bare Tenders
